        "content": "<p>In the later part of <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathematics_in_lean/C06_Structures.html#defining-structures\">section 6.1. Defining structures</a>, it appears that a subsection has been mistakenly typeset together with the previous subsection due to the latter ending with a separate <code>SOLUTIONS-/</code> without <code>/-EXAMPLES</code></p>\n<p>I tried adding a blank line before <code>SOLUTIONS: -/</code>, and it resolved the problem.</p>\n<p><a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/epknlSNQUrNBkdMNKDowHfEL/prt.png\">prt.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/epknlSNQUrNBkdMNKDowHfEL/prt.png\" title=\"prt.png\"><img data-original-dimensions=\"1795x1084\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/3121/epknlSNQUrNBkdMNKDowHfEL/prt.png/840x560.webp\"></a></div>",
